owohl natur- als auch geisteswissenschaftliche Sichtweisen in einer übergreifenden Theorie der Zeit. Physik, Psychologie, Biologie, Philosophie und Medizin fi nden im invers-entropischen Zeitpfeil gemeinsame theoretische Grundlagen eines Weltverständnisses. Das Verständnis der wirklichen Fließrichtung der Zeit ordnet die Welt neu. Es leitet den Leser zu einem begründeten, weil aufgeklärten Optimismus.  aThis volume is the first to incorporate perspectives from both science and the humanities into a comprehensive theory of time. In the inverse-entropic arrow of time, physics, biology, philosophy, and medicine share the theoretical principles of one understanding of the world. Understanding the real direction in which time flows restructures the world. It gives the reader cause for well-founded, enlightened optimism.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mai 2023) 4aBig-Bang Theorie. 4aEntstehung des Lebens. 4aPsychologie. 4aRaumzeit. 4aUrknall. 4aZeitreisen. 7aSCIENCE / Physics / Relativity.2bisacsh  aBig-Bang Theory.  aOrigin of Life.  aPsychology.  aSpacetime.  aTime Travel.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1z978311076682008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chemistry, Mat.Sc, Geosc 2022z9783110993219oZDB-23-DPC0 cEPUBz97831107893860 cprintz978311078927040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311078935540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110789355423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110789355/original  a978-3-11-076682-0  DG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1b2022  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-all